with some background information on triacs. I’ve shown how to implement phase angle control with a PIC and also how to calculate the RMS voltage of the output. I hope I’ve been able to explain this extremely important topic to you clearly and hope that you can now successfully build your own power control circuits using phase angle control with triacs.\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;\"\u003E\u003C\/span\u003E\u003C\/div\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cb\u003EReference Book:\u003C\/b\u003E\u003C\/u\u003E\u003Cbr \/\u003EOne of the best books for understanding the theory behind phase angle control is \"POWER ELECTRONICS - CIRCUITS, DEVICES AND APPLICATIONS\" by Muhammad H. Rashid. If you want to learn more about thyristors or phase angle control, I recommend reading this book for more info."},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/tahmidmc.blogspot.com\/feeds\/747712985286629673\/comments\/default","title":"Post Comments"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/tahmidmc.blogspot.com\/2013\/06\/power-control-with-thyristor-phase.html#comment-form","title":"53 Comments"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/6338993703407602171\/posts\/default\/747712985286629673"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/6338993703407602171\/posts\/default\/747712985286629673"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"http:\/\/tahmidmc.blogspot.com\/2013\/06\/power-control-with-thyristor-phase.html","title":"AC Power Control with Thyristor: Phase Angle Control using triac with PIC16F877A"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"Tahmid"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/09117804893438710050"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"32","height":"32"